EscapeHatchInitiateExitTest
├── given caller is not in candidate set
│   └── it should revert {EscapeHatch__NotInCandidateSet}
└── given caller is in candidate set
    ├── given caller status is not ACTIVE
    │   └── it should revert {EscapeHatch__InvalidStatus}
    └── given caller status is ACTIVE
        ├── when current time is before next freeze timestamp
        │   ├── it should call selectCandidates
        │   ├── it should remove caller from active candidates
        │   ├── it should set caller status to EXITING
        │   ├── it should set exitableAt to current timestamp
        │   └── it should emit CandidateExitInitiated event
        └── when current time is at or after next freeze timestamp
            ├── given caller is selected as proposer during selectCandidates
            │   └── it should revert {EscapeHatch__NotInCandidateSet}
            └── given caller is not selected as proposer during selectCandidates
                ├── it should call selectCandidates
                ├── it should remove caller from active candidates
                ├── it should set caller status to EXITING
                ├── it should set exitableAt to first epoch after next hatch
                └── it should emit CandidateExitInitiated event
